title: Human and Changed Behavior  (Charlamagne and Travis Scott Sit Down)
itunes:title: Human and Changed Behavior  (Charlamagne and Travis Scott Sit Down)
description:
Today on the show we aired Charlamagne's sit down with Travis Scott, where they spoke about the tragedy that happened at his Astro festival in Houston, and his feelings and thoughts of what to do moving forward. After the one on one discussion, we took calls from our listeners to hear their thoughts on what Travis had to say about the event.
